 to help Anne jump across a gap by having her spring off of a giant [[Cat tails|cattail]]. Anne ends up flying far away and Sprig hops on to join her.\n| LineColor       = 7CFC00\n}}\n}}\n\n===''Wild Amphibia''===\nIn the style of nature documentaries, Soggy Joe introduces the viewer to a variety of strange creatures in Amphibia. After Soggy Joe is done reviewing each one, he will reveal a fictional promotion that is associated with him.\n\n{{Episode table\n| total_width     = \n| background      = #E952FF\n| overall         = 10\n| title           = \n| airdate         = 30\n| airdateT        = Online release date\n| episodes        =\n\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 1\n| Title           = Rhino Beetle\n| OriginalAirDate = {{start date|2019|11|13}}\n| ShortSummary    = Soggy Joe reviews the Rhino Beetle seen in \"Hop-Popular.\"\n| LineColor       = E952FF\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 2\n| Title           = Killer Tomatoes\n| OriginalAirDate = {{start date|2019|11|20}}\n| ShortSummary    = Soggy Joe reviews the Killer Tomatoes from \"Hop Luck.\"\n| LineColor       = E952FF\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 3\n| Title           = Kitty\n| OriginalAirDate = {{start date|2019|11|27}}\n| ShortSummary    = Soggy Joe reviews the caterpillar from \"The Domino Effect.\"\n| LineColor       = E952FF\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 4\n| Title           = Praying Mantis\n| OriginalAirDate = {{start date|2019|12|4}}\n| ShortSummary    = Soggy Joe reviews the praying mantis from \"Anne or Beast?\"\n| LineColor       = E952FF\n}}\n}}\n\n==Broadcast==\n''Amphibia'' made its first international debut in [[Disney Channel (Canada)|Canada]] on June 22, 2019. The series also airs repeats on [[Disney XD|Disney XD USA]].{{Citation needed|date=October 2019}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\"\n|+ International\n! scope=\"col\" | Country\n! scope=\"col\" | Release date\n|-\n| {{flagicon|CAN}} [[Disney Channel (Canada)|Canada]]\n| scope=\"row